{"tid":208714,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"嚴 選 8 大 狐 狸 精 ！","createTime":"2017-04-19T16:55:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-07T14:38:41.000Z","uid":53178,"like":209,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e238f85b206c1646364786ba2f5655017eb356d1","tid":208714,"uid":53178,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T16:55:33.000Z","msg":"最近狐狸精當道，我大美人手執打妖棒，同大家一齊滅妖！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>1  楊愛瑾</strong></span><br />\n<br />\nMiki 介入永安太子爺郭永淳同前妻伍智恆婚姻已非舊聞，屬元祖級狐狸精九尾狐仙品種，經年累月修練致樣子溫純，內裡凶殘！早年精通各項邪術，先吸盡前妻陽氣令其慘變皮包骨不似人形後，仍意猶未盡，上年餅碎姊妹Kary流產剛剛佢就懷孕，令人懷疑有人用邪術令某人流產，易轉胎神！此女與蘇妲己齊名，是一件不折不扣，違害人間嘅邪花！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/37i453b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F37i453b.jpg&h=dee3426a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>2  何雁詩</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n新晉狐妖何雁詩近日以狐狸尾巴，一野Fing走賤男牙flirt未婚妻。事件曝光初期，硬屍被記者問到係咪同牙flirt拍拖時，以風騷挑釁tone講出「你覺得係咪係，唔係咪唔係囉」，將狐狸霸地盤習性表露無遺！可惜事件令其形象一落千丈，近日終於忍唔住喺IG post 話自己被人cyberbully，又話自己都有感受，將狐狸精入門級招式「楚楚可憐」發揮得淋漓盡致。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9is59h9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9is59h9.jpg&h=3a6ea9d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>3  苟芸慧</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n係呀，係連登仔都打過J嘅苟芸慧呀。當年肥苟「攻城」不果，俾熊黛林用「打苟棒」打到成隻落水狗咁，雖然最後兩敗俱傷，但苟芸慧自此形象插水，仲搞到暴脹，直到而家時不時仲會消費返件事嚟搏同情，狐狸精一世都係狐狸精。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/34990Gz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F34990Gz.jpg&h=70fe4aac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>4  郭羡妮</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n狐狸狐妮，點少得郭羨妮？當年狐妮同陶大宇拍《學警出更》假戲真做，要求加咀戲，搞到人地7年婚姻玩完。事實上，郭羨妮早年喺大陸拍劇時，已被人影到隨地痾屎痾尿。由於狐狸係一種野獸，就地解決乃人之常情。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/es0t8j9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fes0t8j9.jpg&h=28c7d303&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fKh3krf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfKh3krf.png&h=7878dc52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>5  朱慧敏</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n朱慧敏，梁榮忠同車，你會聯想起啲咩？當然係車震啦！當年梁榮忠用96小時連食3女，成績彪炳！而車震朱慧敏就成為事件中嘅導火線，逼使正印鍾麗淇急飛梁榮忠。雖然朱慧敏多次話自己並唔知對方有女朋友，但牛唔飲水係唔會㩒得牛頭低，野性嘅朱慧敏將狐狸精愛刺激嘅特性發揮得活靈活現。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jppWr6V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjppWr6V.jpg&h=f8b1c201&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jzwS28N.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjzwS28N.jpg&h=ff89c886&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>6  馬賽</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n愛情無分性別，狐狸精亦唔一定要勾引雄性！淫娃馬賽早年被爆同TB汪子琦遊上海，硬撬富婆Laura牆腳！狐狸精托世的馬賽更主動喺酒店拍下艷舞片，仲令汪子琦同「老婆」離婚。TB汪同Laura經歷7年風風雨雨，最後換嚟，竟然係婚戒被馬賽沒收；而Laura更要出律師信要求離婚。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vr6p5Q3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fvr6p5Q3.jpg&h=783c0c24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>7  林燕玲</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n小飛俠09年被壹週刊影到同人夫會計師龔耀輝，於數碼港艾美酒店爆房斷正！記者及後搵到龔太當面對質，龔太當場不知所措，且開始眼泛淚光：「你想我點講，我唔知點講呀」之後她咬咬牙，使自己冷靜後再說：「呢一刻你問我，身為女人，我當然係好傷心，但我都唔知有乜。總之，我無諗過離婚，你等我清靜嚇先，唔該。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2vpEvj9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2vpEvj9.jpg&h=2eda1572&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i53.fastpic.ru/big/2013/0201/82/b2e7553071d94814efa160a844e43382.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi53.fastpic.ru%2Fbig%2F2013%2F0201%2F82%2Fb2e7553071d94814efa160a844e43382.gif&h=15bf9460&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>8  周嘉儀</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n早年有雜誌揭發前TVB主播周嘉儀同已婚嘅許方輝關係曖昧，被人影到喺車上親暱，記者打電話畀事件主角時，男方唔聽電話，女方就剩係講咗句：「我無嘢講！」。最慘係曾任亞視主播嘅許太陳佩琳，在老公偷食後，一度連人帶狗漏夜搬離愛巢。據悉，男方事後花咗大半年時間先氹番老婆，雨過天青。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bjy22mg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fbjy22mg.jpg&h=de4097c8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b61dd4ace8fc8837f72d7255e7af6ad68a885c59","tid":208714,"uid":53178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T17:11:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bfef3b4688c3e849857db9ffb09b1383a68fc6d","tid":208714,"uid":14230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T17:18:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e33e63fa3d8626984a42fe079c6eff13e507cab3","tid":208714,"uid":77400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T17:21:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8ba9e45d3d37000db67f7cbbe5bd6e4c1a0ce28","tid":208714,"uid":25514,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T17:29:37.000Z","msg":"好耐冇見過爆房玲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21778a5bedbdd3537613f68acc180bd637d7f9de","tid":208714,"uid":61675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T17:30:52.000Z","msg":"精彩"},{"pid":"99aad36401ca605ec218681b3f4c62256d07a37a","tid":208714,"uid":2795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T17:33:33.000Z","msg":"無西女人同ada 0分"},{"pid":"e22bd7f7b6afd162b6fb0b3ef3563887441f53c4","tid":208714,"uid":28590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T17:39:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b87005d60e857afc88b2804a12684e7fe5f5277","tid":208714,"uid":16029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T01:25:4